description: This file defines a mock class 'CloudStoreImplementationMock' for testing, which inherits from multiple interfaces related to a cloud storage system, and uses Google Mock to mock methods for store operations.

classes.name: CloudStoreImplementationMock
classes.description: A mock class implementing multiple storage-related interfaces for unit testing various store behaviors.

methods.name: Register
methods.description: Mocks registration of notifications for the IStore and IStore2 interfaces.

methods.name: Unregister
methods.description: Mocks unregistration of notifications for the IStore and IStore2 interfaces.

methods.name: SetValue
methods.description: Mocks setting a value in the store with namespace and key.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mocks retrieving a value from the store.

methods.name: DeleteKey
methods.description: Mocks deleting a key from the store.

methods.name: DeleteNamespace
methods.description: Mocks deleting a namespace from the store.

methods.name: SetValue
methods.description: Mocks setting a value with scope, namespace, key, value, and TTL.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mocks retrieving a scoped value with storage size and TTL.

methods.name: GetKeys
methods.description: Mocks retrieving keys within a scope and namespace.

methods.name: GetNamespaces
methods.description: Mocks retrieving namespaces within a scope.

methods.name: GetStorageSizes
methods.description: Mocks retrieving storage sizes within a scope.

methods.name: GetNamespaceStorageLimit
methods.description: Mocks retrieving the storage limit for a namespace.

methods.name: SetNamespaceStorageLimit
methods.description: Mocks setting the storage limit for a namespace.
